OL,3,CFallout from the budget from a tourism
OL,4,Clevy to inheritance tax for farmers
OL,6,FOn Around The House this month,
OL,7,FPolitical Correspondent Tom Sheldrick
OL,8,Fput it to former Conservative MP for
OL,9,FCarlsile John Stevenson that most
OL,10,Ffarmers would escape the tax, given
OL,11,Fthe #1million threshold.
OL,13,FIn response Mr Stevenson said: "Some
OL,14,Fwill, but a lot of farmers will be
OL,15,Faffected by it because what you forget
OL,16,Fis that they are asset-rich in some
OL,17,Fways, but income-poor."
OL,19,FHe added: "We mustn't lose sight of
OL,20,Fthe fact that farming is really a
OL,21,Fvital part of our long-term security."
